reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Got this shoe rack on sale and figured even if it was mediocre I wouldn’t be out much, but I’m honestly really impressed! Lightweight and easy to put together - it’s perfect for my kids shoes and seems pretty durable too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Shelf to organize your closet!!!
reviews.reviewText: Great product! Easy to assemble, sturdy and perfect size to fit in my closet! Highly recommend!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars quality and reasonable price
reviews.reviewText: I'm pleased with the quality and price, so I've ordered it twice. The only complaint is that there are three shelf fabric sheets were damaged on the top next to the box opening area. They look like cut damage. There is no protective material on the shelf sheets, so may be damaged when opening it. I want to send a message to the seller if they can send me a replacement for damaged shelf fabric sheets, but the site only allows me to return the items for a full refund which I don't intend to. I hope that the seller can send me three new shelf fabric sheets for the damaged part.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Exactly as pictured.
reviews.reviewText: I loved this shoe rack. It was exactly as described and pictured and sturdy. Easy to put together 10-15 min. I’m only knocking a star off because it was missing a piece.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lots of storage
reviews.reviewText: Great shoe rack for storage. It’s not the prettiest thing in the world but it can hold a ton of shoes in not a lot of space. It is somewhat challenging to assemble just because it’s so tight but once assembled it’s very sturdy. Overall great value if you’re needing more storage but don’t care a ton about the aesthetics

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Functioning! Looks great and organized!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I’ve been wanting to organize my shoes for a while. It’s such an upgrade from my old shoe rack. I decided to split this in half (5/5), so it’s not too tall.I’ve assembled too many IKEA furnitures and furnitures in general, and I’d have to say I hate to assemble this. No, it’s not hard to do, and the instruction is more than clear. It hurt my hands so much doing this because it’s so tight and hard to push each one into the frame! It slipped once and now my hands are scratched!But it looks great! I loved it. For $16, it’s good, functioning, and making my shoes look more organized! With all the shoes on, it looks very beautiful. I can even put some shoe inserts for heels and sandals, and it holds up very well. It is also very sturdy and durable.This rack is very lightweight. Easy to disassemble if you need to store or move. It’s very easy to carry around for sure! I didn’t miss any parts. In fact, I’ve some parts left once I was done.Nobody can really guess how much this rack is, without me telling them. They thought it’s more expensive.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This shoe rack is great! I was able to fit so many shoes! I wear a size 5.5-6 and I was able to fit four pairs of tennis shoes on one Shelf and four-six pairs of heals on the other..... & flip flops a bunch lol....was also able to stack my boot boxes as well! Assembling wasn't too bad at all. It looks really intimidating when you first open the box cuz there's so many pieces. But it's not bad. My husband did help me though

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Missing a connector
reviews.reviewText: Rather flimsy due to all the press fit plastic 4-way connectors. Also missing one of the connectors so unable to assemble all 10 shelves. Returns are a PIA so I'll just make do with the 9 shelves I can assemble.
Everything great, just lots of pieces to put together.

I am using this in my craft/sun room, I needed extra shelves , the stuff that is going on the shelves isn't real heavy so its perfect for me, took a few hours to put together, but looks great and just fits in perfect

reviews.reviewTitle: Sturdy so far, but really difficult to assemble
reviews.reviewText: Took me hours to assemble! The connectors and pipes don’t fit perfectly and I had to force every piece (40pcs of connectors in total) in snugly so it sits flat on the floor - prepare to set aside some time and space to put it together. Otherwise happy with the purchase, rack seems sturdy.
It is good for the price, but missing pieces.
